title: Graffiti Sublime Coffee
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A coffee shop with vegan milk choice for all beverages (soy, almond, & hemp milk) plus has fonuts (vegan donut), paleta cold pressed juices, sandwiches, salads. You get 90 minutes of Wi-Fi with purchase. It's a creative place to work  or just hang out by the fire and check out the art hanging on the walls.
